data.text:
2012: Did not appear in any contests.

2011: Played in eight games as a freshman … Caught two passes for 11 yards.

Before Merrimack: Attended Tilton Academy in 2010 after graduating from Grant High School in Portland, Oregon … Believed to be first Merrimack football player ever from Oregon … Caught 58 receptions for 1,176 yards and 12 touchdown at Tilton … Made 55 tackles, forced four fumbles, and picked off eight passes on defense … Returned a punt and a kickoff for a touchdown.

Personal: Civil Engineering major at Merrimack.

CAREER HIGHS

Receptions: 1, Stonehill, 10/22/11 ; at Southern Connecticut, 11/12/2011

Receiving yards: 6, at Southern Connecticut, 11/12/2011 (1 receptions)

Long reception: 6, at Southern Connecticut, 11/12/2011

All-purpose yards: 6, at Southern Connecticut, 11/12/2011
